E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1212','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-29/716d0e2f0c124221909fd999742f341e.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"28\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，嘉鱼县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动现场会在高铁岭镇召开。会议通报了全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动进展情况，并对下一阶段&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作进行了具体的安排部署。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，副县长魏萍等出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">李国光在讲话中指出，我县开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动以来，驻村&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组、县直各部门、各级干部群众踊跃在人力、物力、财力上给予了大力支持，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作成效显著。新年伊始，全县各级各部门要进一步统一思想，明确责任，加大宣传力度，根据拟定的目标任务，加强检查督办，强力推进全县塘堰整治、沟渠清淤等农田水利基础设施建设再上新台阶。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏朝东主持会议。他要求各镇各部门抢抓晴好天气，多争取群众支持，充分利用&ldquo;以奖代补&rdquo;政策，深入开展小农水建设整治，着力改善农业生产条件，掀起我县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动新的高潮。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏萍总结了我县第一阶段&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作取得的成绩，并就下一步工作进行了具体的安排部署。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会前，全体与会人员深入到官桥镇石鼓岭村、官桥村，高铁岭镇白果树村、八斗角村等多处&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;整治现场进行了参观指导。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，截止</span><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"26\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，我县已开工各类工程项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">566</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，占申报项目的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">98.8%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，投入各类机械</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">730</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余台（套），投入劳力</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万余人次，完成土石方</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">452.6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万方，完成投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2220.4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。目前，全县已完成塘堰整治和小农水建设项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">406</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，占计划的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">79.1%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-29/153d833347d6dd80680b4b3b6d525fcd.jpg\\\\\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><br />\r\n整修一新的八斗角村二组&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1209','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-28/c6ffebb810d71dd048aaf157dc56aec6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">剪彩仪式<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-28/6161b0c3d587432dd2c61d6e5c9f26ed.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">庆典现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日，位于县经济开发区内的武汉新联大生物有限公司隆重举行新厂落成庆典仪式。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，县人大副主任贺隆君，副县长许隆高等出席庆典仪式并剪彩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">许隆高代表县委、县政府向武汉新联大生物有限公司新厂落成表示热烈祝贺。他说，近年来，我县把&ldquo;加快发展&rdquo;作为第一要务，探索实施了&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;发展战略，坚持招商引资&ldquo;一号工程&rdquo;，切实加大基础设施投入，拉大园区框架，完善园区功能，优化经济发展环境，构筑招商引资平台，制定了一系列引商、惠商、安商、富商的政策，吸引了大批省内外客商来我县投资兴业。他表示，县委、县政府将一如既往、不遗余力地为项目建设和企业发展保驾护航，为企业更好更快发展提供优质服务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">武汉新联大生物有限公司董事长童庆平对嘉鱼县委、县政府的大力支持表示衷心感谢，同时表示将继续做大做强，打造一支&ldquo;诚信、合作、高效、创新&rdquo;的企业队伍。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县招商局局长张红群主持庆典仪式。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，武汉新联大生物有限公司占地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">145</span>亩，是以兽药生产经营为主的高新技术企业，并通过国家<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">GMP</span>兽药生产企业验收，现有粉剂、散剂、预混剂等多条生产线。该公司以华中农业大学、南京农业大学、长江大学为技术背景，与华农药理研究室紧密合作，生产的兽药赢得各地专业养殖户的一致认可和好评。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1210','79','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-27/33c6215e33921e7a922561d231ef1130.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">奠基现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>日上午，洁丽雅集团嘉鱼产业基地奠基庆典仪式在县经济开发区隆重举行。咸宁市委常委、市纪委书记王远鹤，咸宁市委常委、副市长王汉桥，咸宁市经信委主任张晓先，县领导熊征宇、余珂等出席仪式。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">洁丽雅集团历经<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>余年的发展，现已成为中国民营企业<span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span>强，亚洲品牌<span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span>强，是国内最大的毛巾生产企业。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2004</span>年，该集团对原省属企业嘉鱼棉纺织厂进行并购重组，创建湖北洁丽雅纺织有限公司。多年来，税收连续稳居全县工业企业前列，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>年税收突破千万元。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">县委书记熊征宇在讲话中指出，洁丽雅集团与嘉鱼携手八年来，为我县经济发展作出了重要贡献，县委、县政府将一如既往、不遗余力地为项目建设和企业发展保驾护航。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">洁丽雅集团董事局主席石昌佳说，在嘉鱼发展的八年，让他们深切地感受到历届县委、县政府始终秉承&ldquo;产业第一，企业家老大&rdquo;的理念和亲商、利商、留商、暖商、敬商的氛围日益浓厚。于是该集团决定继续在我县扩大投资，在经济开发区创建洁丽雅集团嘉鱼品牌产业基地。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">据了解，该项目占地<span lang=\"EN-US\">430</span>亩，建设<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>万锭高档毛巾特种纱和年产<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.5</span>万吨高档毛巾现代化生产线。项目规划总投资<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>亿元，产业基地建成后，将年新增工业产值<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>亿元，提供就业岗位<span lang=\"EN-US\">7000</span>个左右。届时将与该集团浙江总部、新疆品牌产业基地一起，在未来五年内，成为世界最大的毛巾生产企业。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">近年来，我县牢固树立大抓项目、抓大项目的理念，按照在谈项目抓签约，签约项目抓开工，开工项目抓进度，建成项目抓进度的思路，形成了建成一批、新建一批、扩建一批、签约一批、在谈一批的&ldquo;五个一批&rdquo;格局。预计今年新增工业税收超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">7000</span>万元，规模工业增加值增幅、工业入库税收增幅、招商引资实际到位资金、工业用电量和用地量五项指标，均居全市各县市区前列，工业经济发展呈现出良好的发展态势。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><o:p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1211','79','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-28/c6ffebb810d71dd048aaf157dc56aec6.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">剪彩仪式<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-28/6161b0c3d587432dd2c61d6e5c9f26ed.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">庆典现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日，位于县经济开发区内的武汉新联大生物有限公司隆重举行新厂落成庆典仪式。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，县人大副主任贺隆君，副县长许隆高等出席庆典仪式并剪彩。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">许隆高代表县委、县政府向武汉新联大生物有限公司新厂落成表示热烈祝贺。他说，近年来，我县把&ldquo;加快发展&rdquo;作为第一要务，探索实施了&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;发展战略，坚持招商引资&ldquo;一号工程&rdquo;，切实加大基础设施投入，拉大园区框架，完善园区功能，优化经济发展环境，构筑招商引资平台，制定了一系列引商、惠商、安商、富商的政策，吸引了大批省内外客商来我县投资兴业。他表示，县委、县政府将一如既往、不遗余力地为项目建设和企业发展保驾护航，为企业更好更快发展提供优质服务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">武汉新联大生物有限公司董事长童庆平对嘉鱼县委、县政府的大力支持表示衷心感谢，同时表示将继续做大做强，打造一支&ldquo;诚信、合作、高效、创新&rdquo;的企业队伍。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">县招商局局长张红群主持庆典仪式。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><font size=\"3\">据悉，武汉新联大生物有限公司占地<span lang=\"EN-US\">145</span>亩，是以兽药生产经营为主的高新技术企业，并通过国家<span lang=\"EN-US\">GMP</span>兽药生产企业验收，现有粉剂、散剂、预混剂等多条生产线。该公司以华中农业大学、南京农业大学、长江大学为技术背景，与华农药理研究室紧密合作，生产的兽药赢得各地专业养殖户的一致认可和好评。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><o:p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1213','285','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-29/716d0e2f0c124221909fd999742f341e.jpg\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"28\" month=\"12\" year=\"2011\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">28</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">，嘉鱼县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动现场会在高铁岭镇召开。会议通报了全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动进展情况，并对下一阶段&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作进行了具体的安排部署。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，副县长魏萍等出席会议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">李国光在讲话中指出，我县开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动以来，驻村&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组、县直各部门、各级干部群众踊跃在人力、物力、财力上给予了大力支持，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作成效显著。新年伊始，全县各级各部门要进一步统一思想，明确责任，加大宣传力度，根据拟定的目标任务，加强检查督办，强力推进全县塘堰整治、沟渠清淤等农田水利基础设施建设再上新台阶。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">魏朝东主持会议。他要求各镇各部门抢抓晴好天气，多争取群众支持，充分利用&ldquo;以奖代补&rdquo;政策，深入开展小农水建设整治，着力改善农业生产条件，掀起我县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动新的高潮。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">魏萍总结了我县第一阶段&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作取得的成绩，并就下一步工作进行了具体的安排部署。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">会前，全体与会人员深入到官桥镇石鼓岭村、官桥村，高铁岭镇白果树村、八斗角村等多处&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;整治现场进行了参观指导。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">据悉，截止</span><st1:chsdate isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"26\" month=\"12\" year=\"2011\" w:st=\"on\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">26</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">，我县已开工各类工程项目</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">566</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">个，占申报项目的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">98.8%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">，投入各类机械</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">730</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">余台（套），投入劳力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3.1</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万余人次，完成土石方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">452.6</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万方，完成投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2220.4</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">万元。目前，全县已完成塘堰整治和小农水建设项目</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">406</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">个，占计划的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">79.1%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-29/153d833347d6dd80680b4b3b6d525fcd.jpg\" /></span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><br />\r\n整修一新的八斗角村二组&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1214','6','庞S','南鄂晚报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">第四次党代会上，谈到嘉鱼未来的发展，嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇信心十足。他说，报告多处提到嘉鱼的发展，咸嘉新城、长江大桥、百里蔬菜长廊、武深高速等项目的实施，必将推动嘉鱼更好更快发展。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" day=\\\\\"7\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，市委书记黄楚平到嘉鱼调研，指出要将嘉鱼建成人人向往之地。熊征宇说，嘉鱼将围绕建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的总体目标，全县上下要紧紧围绕既定的总体目标和战略重点，着力推进&ldquo;实力嘉鱼、活力嘉鱼、魅力嘉鱼、合力嘉鱼&rdquo;四个新嘉鱼的建设。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;嘉鱼县滨江含湖，山清水秀，又紧邻大武汉，区位条件优越，沿江资源丰富，人居环境优美。&rdquo;熊征宇说，嘉鱼要做大做强优势产业，依托现有产业基础，重点打造纺织、建材、钢管制造、精细化工、食品加工、新能源等年产值过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的六大产业集群，深入推进&ldquo;一区多园&rdquo;、产业集群、中小企业成长倍增和精品名牌&ldquo;四大发展战略&rdquo;，着力构建经济开发区、镇级工业园、咸嘉新城&ldquo;三驾马车&rdquo;，建设现代农业示范区，打造优秀旅游目的地，加快发展现代商贸物流产业。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">嘉鱼还将抢抓武汉城市圈、武汉新港建设以及沿海地区产业转移机遇，在招商引资上下功夫，力争今后五年，全县招商引资到位资金超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，实际利用外资超过</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万美元，投资过亿元项目</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个以上，引进中国</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强企业</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5-10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家，在引进世界</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">500</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">强企业上实现零的突破。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">做优做美城乡环境，美化城乡人居环境，提升城乡发展承载力；做精做细社会管理，着力为民办实事、办好事，努力让人民群众共享改革发展成果&hellip;&hellip;熊征宇说，这些都是今后嘉鱼县在经济社会发展方面要做的事情。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">今后五年，是嘉鱼县全面建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的重要五年。熊征宇表示，力争通过五年的努力，使嘉鱼的县域经济综合实力迈入全省&ldquo;第一方阵&rdquo;，跨入湖北经济强县行列，主要经济指标翻番，实现县域经济总量、居民幸福指数、生态环境质量、依法治县水平明显提高。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1215','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2011]133</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">在县第十七届人民代表大会第一次会议上，县政府提出了未来五年和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年的奋斗目标、主要措施和政府着力抓好的重要工作。为了进一步明确工作责任、推动工作落实，现将《政府工作报告》确定的未来五年和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年重要工作责任分解如下：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、未来五年，努力建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）全县经济社会发展总体目标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">县域经济总量明显提高。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">努力实现&ldquo;<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"33221\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"&rdquo;\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">33221</span>&rdquo;</st1:chmetcnv>目标，即全县生产总值达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>亿元，规模工业企业超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>家；财政总收入达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亿元，年税收过千万元企业超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>家；全社会固定资产投资五年累计完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>亿元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、许隆高；主要责任单位：经信局、统计局、财政局、地税局、国税局、发改局等）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">居民幸福指数明显提高。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，城镇居民人均可支配收入达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26000</span>元，农民人均纯收入达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">14000</span>元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、魏萍；主要责任单位：人社局、农业局、统计局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">生态环境质量明显提高。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">全县单位生产总值综合能耗累计下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>，耕地占补保持基本平衡。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、李德炳、许隆高、魏萍；主要责任单位：发改局、国土局、农业局、经信局等）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）实施工业倍增工程，推动县域经济大发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">壮大园区平台。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加快修编经济开发区和镇级工业园总体规划，完善功能分区，不断提高园区承载力和竞争力。将官桥、鱼岳、新街工业园纳入经济开发区统一规划建设，力争园区建成面积达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>平方公里。到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，全县园区规模经济占规模工业的比重达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90%</span>，园区经济年税收实现<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>亿元以上。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、李德炳、许隆高；主要责任单位：开发区、发改局、经信局、国土局、规划执法局、各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">培植优势产业。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">围绕钢管制造、纺织、食品加工、建材、新能源、精细化工等支柱产业，着力打造<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>个年产值过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>亿元的重点产业集群。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争年税收过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>万元企业达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>家、过千万元企业达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>家、过亿元企业新增<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>家，上市公司实现零的突破。到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争高新技术产业增加值占地区生产总值的比重达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>；全县资源综合利用企业达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>家以上，开展清洁生产审核的规模企业达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">75%</span>以上；培育<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2-3</span>个中国名牌或中国驰名商标，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>个以上湖北名牌商标。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：许隆高；主要责任单位：开发区、经信局、招商局、工商局、技术监督局、科技局、环保局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">依托特色招商。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，全县招商引资到位资金要超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>亿元，实际利用外资超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8000</span>万美元，投资过亿元项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>个以上，力争引进中国<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>强企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5-10</span>家，在引进世界<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>强企业上实现零的突破。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌、许隆高；主要责任单位：开发区、经信局、招商局、商务局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）实施农业转型工程，推动农村经济大繁荣。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加强农田水利建设。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">重点推进江堤、湖堤综合整治，加快<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><v:shapetype id=\\\\\"_x0000_t75\\\\\" stroked=\\\\\"f\\\\\" filled=\\\\\"f\\\\\" path=\\\\\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\\\\\" o:preferrelative=\\\\\"t\\\\\" o:spt=\\\\\"75\\\\\" coordsize=\\\\\"21600,21600\\\\\"> <v:stroke joinstyle=\\\\\"miter\\\\\"></v:stroke><v:formulas><v:f eqn=\\\\\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"sum @0 1 0\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"sum 0 0 @1\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @2 1 2\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @3 21600 pixelWidth\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @3 21600 pixelHeight\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"sum @0 0 1\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @6 1 2\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @7 21600 pixelWidth\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"sum @8 21600 0\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"prod @7 21600 pixelHeight\\\\\"></v:f><v:f eqn=\\\\\"sum @10 21600 0\\\\\"></v:f></v:formulas><v:path o:connecttype=\\\\\"rect\\\\\" gradientshapeok=\\\\\"t\\\\\" o:extrusionok=\\\\\"f\\\\\"></v:path><o:lock aspectratio=\\\\\"t\\\\\" v:ext=\\\\\"edit\\\\\"></o:lock></v:shapetype><v:shape id=\\\\\"_x0000_i1025\\\\\" type=\\\\\"#_x0000_t75\\\\\" style=\\\\\"width: 12pt; height: 15pt\\\\\"><v:imagedata o:title=\\\\\"餐\\\\\" src=\\\\\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1\\\\01clip_image001.jpg\\\\\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span>子湖中型水库和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>座小型水库除险加固，推进沿江泵站涵闸更新改造，加快斧头湖等重点湖泊及金水河等中小河流治理。实施三湖连江灌区续建工程三期，完成陆水和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><v:shape id=\\\\\"_x0000_i1026\\\\\" type=\\\\\"#_x0000_t75\\\\\" style=\\\\\"width: 12pt; height: 15pt\\\\\"> <v:imagedata o:title=\\\\\"餐\\\\\" src=\\\\\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1\\\\01clip_image001.jpg\\\\\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span>子湖灌区续建项目；实施永逸泵站等中型泵站更新改造和余码头泵站增容；因地制宜兴建中小型水利设施，建设山丘区&ldquo;五小水利&rdquo;。做好斧头湖、西凉湖与长江的水系连通规划建设。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：魏萍；主要责任单位：水利局、农业局、水产局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">发展特色生态农业。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以湖北大禾现代设施农业为样板，新建万亩现代设施农业生产基地，建设水产标准化健康养殖基地；大力发展油茶经济林，新建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>万亩油茶木本油料基地；抓好万亩蓖麻基地建设，积极创建全国蓖麻良种育种基地。到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争全县实现农业增加值<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25</span>亿元，新认证绿色食品品牌<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>个、有机食品品牌<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个，申报注册嘉鱼农产品地理标识商标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：魏萍；主要责任单位：农办、农业局、工商局、水产局、林业局、各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">增强农民增收能力。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争全县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50%</span>以上农民参加各类农民专业合作组织，农副产品加工企业超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>家，其中培育省级龙头企业<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>家以上、国家级龙头企业实现零的突破。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：魏萍；主要责任单位：农办、农业局、各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）实施旅游跨越工程，推动发展方式大转变。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加快景区规划建设。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加快开发仙人洞、七星洞、沿江沙洲湿地等旅游资源；逐年恢复建设吴王行祠、孔明取箭所、岳公亭等历史文化古迹。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌、李德炳；主要责任单位：规划执法局、文体新局、旅游局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">11.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">提升旅游服务水平。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">扶持旅游产品生产企业发展，做精做强做活</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">洲湾鱼圆、嘉鱼麻糖、二乔木枕等地方特色旅游产品。加强旅游配套设施，规划建设购物、娱乐、美食一条街。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：旅游局、规划执法局、相关镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加快旅游宣传营销。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争全县建成<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"5\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"a\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5A</span></st1:chmetcnv>级景点<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>个，四星级酒店<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3-5</span>家、五星级酒店<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>家，实现年接待游客<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>万人次，旅游总收入超过<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亿元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：旅游局）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">13.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">促进地域文化发展。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，力争全县文化事业发展主要指标居全市先进行列，文化产业增加值占地区生产总值的比重达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5%</span>。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌；主要责任单位：文体新局）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）实施城市宜居工程，推动市容市貌大提升。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">14.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以战略眼光规划城市。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，县城区面积达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>平方公里，常住人口达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>万人，城镇绿化覆盖率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30%</span>以上，把嘉鱼建设成为武汉城市圈内的山水园林城、绿色生态县。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳、魏萍；主要责任单位：住建局、规划执法局、林业局、鱼岳镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以现代理念管理城市。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">认真执行城市&ldquo;两禁&rdquo;决定，加大拆违力度，打击私搭乱建行为，努力打造整洁、优美、有序的城市环境，为&ldquo;三城同创&rdquo;打下坚实基础。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：住建局、规划执法局、国土局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以联动发展统筹城乡。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">积极推进新农村建设，完善镇村基础设施和环境综合整治。完成官桥村、四邑村、净堡村&ldquo;迁村腾地&rdquo;、&ldquo;整村推进&rdquo;项目，加快界石村新农村建设步伐。同时，每年选择<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>个条件成熟的村，实施中心村合并或整村推进，力争五年完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5-10</span>个整村新农村建设，改善农村人居环境。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳、魏萍；主要责任单位：农办、农业局、水利局、畜牧局、住建局、林业局、国土局、各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）实施交通畅通工程，推动基础设施大改善。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">17.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完善交通网络体系。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">全力抓好嘉鱼长江大桥和武深高速（嘉鱼段）项目建设，积极实施咸潘一级公路、武赤线（官桥段）一级公路工程，尽快实现陆口大桥建成通车。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、李德炳；主要责任单位：发改局、交通局、相关镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">18.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">建设物流大平台。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">规划建设嘉鱼长江大桥临江物流园、潘家湾物流集聚园，努力把嘉鱼建成鄂南物流集散地、武汉新港中转站。加快嘉鱼港区建设，重点做好临江山综合码头、中港码头、核电重件码头等项目建设改造，加快推进潘家湾、鱼岳等港区集装箱码头建设，使嘉鱼港区年吞吐量达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>万吨。到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2016</span>年，组建培育<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3-5</span>个具有一定实力的综合商贸物流企业集团，物流业总产值达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>亿元以上。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、饶自斌、李德炳；主要责任单位：发改局、规划执法局、交通局、商务局、相关镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">19.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加强能源网络信息建设。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">推进&ldquo;西气东输&rdquo;管道燃气工程和城区供气管网工程建设，推进电信网、广播电视网、互联网三网融合，提高网络覆盖率。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌、李德炳、许隆高；主要责任单位：住建局、广电局、电信公司等）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年，围绕目标抓落实，努力实现跨越发展的良好开局<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;四增两降两突破&rdquo;，</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">即全县生产总值增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18%</span>，地方一般预算收入增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25%</span>，社会消费品零售总额增长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20%</span>，农民人均纯收入增加<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>元以上；单位生产总值综合能耗下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5%</span>，出生人口性别比下降<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个百分点；规模工业增加值突破<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>亿元，全社会固定资产投资额突破<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">120</span>亿元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、饶自斌、许隆高、魏萍；主要责任单位：发改局、统计局、经信局、计生局、农业局、财政局、商务局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">21.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一个大迈步。</span></b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2012</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">年，全县规模以上工业企业总产值达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">296</span>亿元，工业增加值达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>亿元。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：许隆高；主要责任单位：开发区、经信局）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">22.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">两个上水平。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">重点抓好三湖连江灌区续建、余码头泵站更新改造二期、农村安全饮水工程以及虎山、神塘两座小型水库除险加固项目建设。积极向上争取<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><v:shape id=\\\\\"_x0000_i1027\\\\\" type=\\\\\"#_x0000_t75\\\\\" style=\\\\\"width: 12pt; height: 15pt\\\\\"> <v:imagedata o:title=\\\\\"餐\\\\\" src=\\\\\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1\\\\01clip_image001.jpg\\\\\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span>子湖灌区、三湖连江灌区三期、水土保持、余码头泵站三期等项目工程。建设界石村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>亩现代设施农业基地；继续实施蔬菜&ldquo;双百工程&rdquo;，大力引进推广农作物新优品种和高新种植模式，在武嘉沿线新建或扩建蔬菜大棚<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>亩，着力打造<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>个集科研、示范、观光于一体的农业科技园。大力发展休闲渔业，在沿湖、沿路、沿山建立配套垂钓场所，建成休闲渔业场所<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>家以上，覆盖养殖面积近万亩。做好海航集团南嘉风情小镇规划设计并组织施工，启动白湖南岸生态产业园和五星级酒店建设，整体规划并启动建设南如禅寺、禅修度假村；积极争取<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><v:shape id=\\\\\"_x0000_i1028\\\\\" type=\\\\\"#_x0000_t75\\\\\" style=\\\\\"width: 12pt; height: 15pt\\\\\"> <v:imagedata o:title=\\\\\"餐\\\\\" src=\\\\\"file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1\\\\01clip_image001.jpg\\\\\"></v:imagedata></v:shape></span>子湖休闲旅游项目纳入湖北重点项目库，做好项目区土地征收、流转及拆迁还建工作。扶持<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>户农家乐经营户发展沿武赤公路乡村旅游，统筹规划好官桥镇旅游名镇创建工作。力争全年接待旅游人数达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>万人（次），旅游综合收入达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>亿元。大力发展商贸物流，力争引进<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1-2</span>家大型商贸集团、商贸中心进驻嘉鱼。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌、李德炳、许隆高、魏萍；主要责任单位：农办、水利局、农业局、旅游局、水产局、规划执法局、旅游局、招商局、商务局及各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">23.</span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三个新突破。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一是启动原化肥厂、热电厂地块城市综合体规划建设，实施樱花南路南段延伸工程，做好殷家坡、鱼岳路、北门路等城区道路改造刷黑工程，完成环湖公园建设，做好园区绿化培植及配套设施完善工程。加快推进城乡环境综合整治。二是完成陆口大桥嘉鱼境内接线和陆舒线改建工程，实施嘉鱼三环线一级公路、嘉鱼中心客运站改扩建和潘家湾物流集聚园区二级站配送中心工程，力争开工建设嘉鱼长江大桥及接线高速项目、武深高速<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">(</span>嘉鱼段<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">)</span>和咸潘一级公路工程。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、李德炳；主要责任单位：发改局、交通局、规划执法局、住建局及相关镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年着力办好十件民生实事<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">24.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">全面实施新型农村基本养老保险，全年城镇新增就业岗位<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5000</span>个。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华；主要责任单位：人社局和各镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">解决<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>万农村人口安全饮水问题，实施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>万亩小型农田水利基础设施建设。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：魏萍；主要责任单位：水利局和相关镇人民政府）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">26.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">开工建设三环线官桥至石矶头段，完成高铁至舒桥公路建设。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：交通局、规划执法局、国土局、鱼岳镇、官桥镇、高铁岭镇人民政府）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">27.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完成县文体会展中心体育馆、篮球场等公共体育设施主体工程建设。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌；主要责任单位：文体新局）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完成县人民医院建设并投入使用。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌；主要责任单位：卫生局、人民医院等）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">29.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">启动县殡仪馆搬迁工程，启动县垃圾处理厂建设。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：熊武华、李德炳、魏萍；主要责任单位：民政局、住建局、规划执法局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">在县城区新建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2-3</span>所公立幼儿园。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：饶自斌；主要责任单位：教育局）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">31.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完成安山至嘉鱼天然气工程建设，力争年内供气。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：住建局）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">32.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完成省政府下达的保障性安居工程建设任务。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：住建局、房管局等）</b><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">33.</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">完成老城区凤凰大道、龙潭大道等主次干道道路刷黑和人行道改造升级工程。<b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\">（主要责任领导：李德炳；主要责任单位：住建局、交通局等）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 217pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一一年十二月二十七</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 217pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 217pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 217pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 217pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 15.5\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1216','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-30/b9cdd6db22c41d69d348de60d774a6be.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">参观潘家湾镇便民服务大厅<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-30/a9ff302cd1e29a58df85538e0ea49ec9.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">参观县国土资源局廉政宣传栏<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日，市纪委常委张文秋带队的市党风廉政建设责任制和惩防体系建设检查考核组来我县检查工作，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">检查考核组一行先后来到潘家湾镇、县国土资源局就党风廉政建设责任制工作的情况进行了详细了解。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">在潘家湾镇便民服务中心大厅里，检查组通过自助电子屏幕，了解到近期各项国家惠农政策和该镇惠农资金的发放情况等内容。该镇党委书记周亚澜介绍说，该镇党务政务村务都会通过电子显示屏、政府网站和公开栏进行定期更新，并且以镇便民服务大厅为龙头，村、居委会便民服务室为基础的便民服务网络，已实现了镇审批和服务的全覆盖，检查组对此表示赞扬。周亚澜还介绍，该镇一直把党风廉政建设与园区建设、农业发展、队伍建设、治庸问责、便民服务、社会稳定、工作实际、长远发展八项实际工作相结合，做到一手抓经济社会发展，一手抓反腐倡廉建设，将工作落到实处并取得了实效。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">走进县国土资源局机关院，随处可见的&ldquo;慎&rdquo;、&ldquo;勤&rdquo;、&ldquo;和&rdquo;、&ldquo;静&rdquo;等国土文化石很快吸引了检查组成员，该局局长吴鹏介绍说，这是为了警示和教育干部职工所设的，用来随时提醒自己要保持谨慎、勤奋等优良品质。据了解，在党风廉政建设工作上该局创新工作体制，创造性地开展&ldquo;十个全覆盖&rdquo;、廉政风险预警防控、党务政务公开等工作。在项目建设中，率先推出廉政保证金制度；大力推行电子政务建设，全面启动了电子政务网上办公；建立廉政风险教育机制，把廉政风险教育融入每周五下午的机关党员干部学习日；推行首问责任制、错案责任追究制、失职追究制等一系列制度。同时，在该局机关院内，还开辟了党务政务公开长廊，制作了图文并茂的党务政务宣传栏，干部职工人手一套《读点经典》，全局上下营造了良好的反腐倡廉氛围。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">检查组一行通过实地查看、听取汇报和查阅资料台账等，认为潘家湾镇和国土资源局这两个被抽查单位都做到了高度重视党风廉政建设工作，并且将这项工作融入了平时实际工作中，不仅抓得全面而且抓得实在，创造了和谐的廉政建设氛围，取得了显著效果。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据悉，接下来检查组还将继续在我县开展民意调查、个别座谈、专题了解等活动，全面了解我县党风廉政建设责任制和惩防体系建设工作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1217','284','汪姝琴、谢浩浩','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2011-12-30/3cd1b8cfba3e3d730e7d12bda8700e1b.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;行政服务中心作为政府形象的展示平台，通过开门评议开展治庸问责工作，进一步提升服务质量和窗口办结效能，为全县经济发展提供优质高效服务&rdquo;。县治庸问责优化发展环境组组长、县政府办副主任、行政服务中心常务副主任来复兴如是说。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">29</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县行政服务中心举办治庸问责开门评议座谈会，主动接受前来参会的两代表一委员、部分企业、群众代表及机关领导评议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，来复兴对中心前期治庸问责工作作了全面深刻的报告。他表示中心开展治庸问责工作以来积极开展治庸问责学习活动，组织窗口工作人员及中心管理人员到江汉区考察调研，并撰写学习心得，取得了明显效果。中心工作纪律、业务水平、服务态度都得到了很大改善。他强调在后期工作中要紧抓治庸问责工作，一是加大宣传力度；二是加强内部管理；三是改进中心办事流程，全面提速提效。希望各代表建言献策，把行政服务中心创建成品牌服务窗口，为嘉鱼全面发展提供优质的服务环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县政协委员温浪林指出，行政服务中心的办事环境、服务态度、工作人员精神面貌得到了整体改善，希望中心在下一步工作中整治&ldquo;两头受理、体外循环&rdquo;的问题，实现真正的&ldquo;一站式&rdquo;服务。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县人大代表李晓芳对行政服务中心的治庸问责工作表示肯定，并提议要优化窗口设置，调剂部门窗口给地税局，方便其更多业务进驻中心。同时建议中心建立办事信息共享平台，压缩审批时限。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">中能锂电负责人任东海表示，行政服务中心召开治庸问责开门评议座谈会意义重大，为企业和百姓提供了一个表达心声的平台。他提出，中心在后期工作中要进一步完善办事流程、简化办事程序、提高办事效率，为客商提供更好、更快、更优的服务。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会后，各代表提交了行政服务中心治庸问责工作调查问卷，为中心治庸问责工作献计献策。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1218','6','黄伟进','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日上午，县政协主席葛婷一行来到新街镇，对该镇拆违控违维稳工作进行督查调研。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">葛婷一行首先听取了该镇党委书记杨新武对拆违控违维稳工作开展情况的汇报，她指出，新街镇紧邻城区，拆违控违工作任务重，压力大，镇党委、政府高度重视，布署周密，措施得力，力度到位，值得肯定。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">葛婷要求县包保科局和新街镇要加强领导，要深入包保对象，进一步摸清&ldquo;两违&rdquo;建筑的基本情况，准确把握违建户的思想动态，认真把政策宣传到位，及时、有效化解新的矛盾和纠纷，确保不出现新增违建事件，不出现越级上访，不出现违建户串联上访等现象。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">随后，葛婷一行深入新街镇何家畈查看两违建筑并走访了包保对象。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1219','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-30/efdbc80970f160089834bcd7059e336f.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">认真填写民意调查表<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日上午，市纪委常委张文秋带队的市党风廉政建设责任制和推进惩防腐败体系建设工作检查考核组在我县开展民意调查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委副书记李国光，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东出席测评会议。李国光指出，这次市委组织的检查考核，是对我县反腐倡廉工作情况的一次集中检查，也是对我县党政领导班子和县级领导干部的一次政治体检。开展民意调查既是及时落实中央、省委和市委关于进一步扩大民主，落实党员干部群众知情权、参与权、表达权和监督权的具体体现，也是改进检查考核方式、提高检查考核结果科学性的重要举措。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李国光要求参加民意调查的人员要以高度的政治责任感，认真阅读、准确把握民意调查表的基本内容，本着对组织负责、对干部负责的态度，坚持党性原则，严肃认真、实事求是地对党政领导班子作出客观公正的评价。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县直部门负责人，及部分县人大代表、政协委员共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>余人，参加了民主测评。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1220','6','李发扬、江开群、舒爱民','咸宁日报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">八年磨一剑，八年圆一梦。嘉鱼以不懈的努力，追寻全国文明县城之梦；以不停的脚步，终于迈进荣誉的大门。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，从北京传来喜讯，第三批全国文明城市名单揭晓，嘉鱼县荣膺&ldquo;全国文明县城&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;创建文明县城，是为了让这个城市的人民生活得更加幸福美好。&rdquo;嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇说，嘉鱼获得的是一个城市的金字招牌和靓丽名片。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">载着梦想启航</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">就在</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2004</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年以前，嘉鱼境内交通基础设施还十分落后，做强工业，发展旅游还只是一个梦，一个痛。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为了彻底改变这种落后的局面，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2004</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼县提出创建文明县城。历届县领导一届接着一届干，一张蓝图画到底，以创建为抓手，以发展为第一要务，强力推动经济建设、城市建设和各项社会事业齐头并进。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2006</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼县经济开发区跻身省级重点开发区，拉开</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里的发展大框架。开发区先后吸引了天津岐丰、浙江盛宇、江苏三木、广州士美、佛山锂电等知名企业落户。各镇级工业园相继形成规模，潘家湾畈湖化工园成功晋级市级化工园区。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2009</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼开发山湖温泉度假区，实现旅游产业&ldquo;零&rdquo;的突破。海航集团斥资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">105</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，整体打造三湖连江核心风景区；长鹿集团投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，开发陆溪渗子湖。嘉鱼旅游彰显出强大的后发优势，如今正朝着旅游强县、全国优秀旅游目的地的目标迈进。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">预计到今年底，嘉鱼可完成生产总值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">108</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，规模工业增加值达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">64</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，地方一般预算收入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4.4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元。而这三项指标，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2005</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年分别只有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">32.36</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">0.9</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">经济飞速发展的同时，嘉鱼先后投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿多元，用于改善城市人居环境，建设幸福之城。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">沙滩浴场、人民公园、二乔公园、沿湖景观带相继建成，免费向市民开放，过去仅有几个公共文体娱乐场所，现在达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多个。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">京港澳高速连接线，武嘉一级公路，城区发展大道、迎宾大道相继建成通车；老城区主次干道刷黑、人行道改造；全面&ldquo;禁麻&rdquo;、&ldquo;禁摩&rdquo;，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多台公交车、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">200</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多台出租车穿街过巷。嘉鱼人民出行更畅通，更方便。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">主次干道全部实施亮化、绿化、美化工程；平安城市视频监控系统覆盖大街小巷；城市生活污水截流管网全面落成，并新建污水处理厂等。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">城市功能越来越完善了，城市越来越美了。以前不知道邀客人来玩什么的嘉鱼人，如今逢年过节，总喜欢请亲戚朋友过来转一转、看一看。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全民参与创建</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">揽获国字号&ldquo;金字招牌&rdquo;，嘉鱼人感到无比豪迈。但翻开</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年创建历史，殊不知，文明创建之初，部分干部有怨气，部分群众不理解。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县直机关单位不仅要出力，还要出钱，行动不力还要受通报批评，不免有怨气。出店占道经营的摊主，遇到创建整治队员，总是有抵触情绪，创建有难度，矛盾重重。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">随着&ldquo;建设人民满意城市&rdquo;目标的提出。一项项民生工程改善人们的生活，一缕缕民生福祉润泽人民心田。创建的实效消解了怨气，赢得了民心。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">少则</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">来万，多则上百万的投入，使县直单位办公条件、服务设施改善了，居住环境改变了，对外形象提升了，收入水平也随着经济的发展逐步提升。创建的怨气没了。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">城市环境看得见、摸得着的变化，让老百姓得到了吃、住、行等方方面面的实惠。群众对创建越来越主动了。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">80</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">岁的胡大爷，每天必做的一件事情就是拿着笔记本到街上转一转，哪里不干净，哪里设施有破损，他都逐一记录下来，然后来到创建办&ldquo;问责&rdquo;。退休干部舒老曾带着自己拍摄的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多张有损城市形象的照片，来到县创建办，提出整改要求和建议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在创建工作中，嘉鱼县建立了整套完善的运行机制，覆盖了企事业单位、学校、社区及社会团体。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多名县级领导挂帅，包路段、包区域，当&ldquo;街长&rdquo;、当&ldquo;路长&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名主要县领导担任县城及周边</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个社区第一书记；</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">220</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名市容监督员走街串巷，乐当&ldquo;和事佬&rdquo;；&ldquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">分钟文明早课&rdquo;成为学生们每天的必修课&hellip;&hellip;</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;现在，不维护创建成果，嘉鱼人民都不答应。&rdquo;县创建全国文明县城指挥部办公室常务副主任雷申会说。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">幸福指数倍增</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">谈及文明创建的成果，&ldquo;老嘉鱼&rdquo;赵帮国一脸幸福地说：&ldquo;没有创建，就没有嘉鱼人民今天舒心惬意的生活环境。&rdquo;</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2004</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼着手创建省级文明县城，次年被省委、省政府命名为&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;，并连续３届获此殊荣。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2009</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼荣获&ldquo;全国平安建设先进县&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级园林县城&rdquo;称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2010</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，获得&ldquo;国家级食品安全示范县&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国绿化模范县&rdquo;称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年初，嘉鱼获评&ldquo;省级卫生县城&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年底，嘉鱼摘得&ldquo;全国文明县城&rdquo;桂冠。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">短短</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年，嘉鱼完成了从一个小城到省级文明卫生县城再到全国文明县城的完美跨越，先后获得全国、省、市文明单位荣誉</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余个。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;蔬菜大县&rdquo;、&ldquo;螃蟹之乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;黄金之乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;t鱼之乡&rdquo;的美誉实至名归。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">嘉鱼人感叹：创建让他们享受到了实实在在的福祉。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">人均纯收入年增</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">700</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">元左右，群众对每年政府承诺实事落实情况测评满意率达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">98%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，群众对政风行风满意率达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">98%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，群众对社会治安满意率达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">96%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">各种内容健康、形式多样、丰富多彩的群众性文体活动越来越多，今年仅在二乔公园就开展了元宵灯会、拔河比赛、歌咏比赛、摄影展、根雕沙龙等活动</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多场。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">过去羡慕武汉、羡慕温泉，如今越来越多的外地客商来到嘉鱼兴业，越来越多的外地务工人员纷纷回乡创业，而且每年都有武汉市民到嘉鱼买房定居。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;全国文明县城的桂冠，不只是一个梦想的实现，对嘉鱼人来说，更是一段幸福新征程的开启。&rdquo;县长余珂说，要巩固好文明创建的成果，真正把嘉鱼建成人人向往的地方。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1221','268','李发扬、江开群、舒爱民','咸宁日报','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">八年磨一剑，八年圆一梦。嘉鱼以不懈的努力，追寻全国文明县城之梦；以不停的脚步，终于迈进荣誉的大门。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日，从北京传来喜讯，第三批全国文明城市名单揭晓，嘉鱼县荣膺&ldquo;全国文明县城&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">&ldquo;创建文明县城，是为了让这个城市的人民生活得更加幸福美好。&rdquo;嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇说，嘉鱼获得的是一个城市的金字招牌和靓丽名片。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">载着梦想启航</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">就在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年以前，嘉鱼境内交通基础设施还十分落后，做强工业，发展旅游还只是一个梦，一个痛。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">为了彻底改变这种落后的局面，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼县提出创建文明县城。历届县领导一届接着一届干，一张蓝图画到底，以创建为抓手，以发展为第一要务，强力推动经济建设、城市建设和各项社会事业齐头并进。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2006</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼县经济开发区跻身省级重点开发区，拉开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">平方公里的发展大框架。开发区先后吸引了天津岐丰、浙江盛宇、江苏三木、广州士美、佛山锂电等知名企业落户。各镇级工业园相继形成规模，潘家湾畈湖化工园成功晋级市级化工园区。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼开发山湖温泉度假区，实现旅游产业&ldquo;零&rdquo;的突破。海航集团斥资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">105</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元，整体打造三湖连江核心风景区；长鹿集团投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">60</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元，开发陆溪渗子湖。嘉鱼旅游彰显出强大的后发优势，如今正朝着旅游强县、全国优秀旅游目的地的目标迈进。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">预计到今年底，嘉鱼可完成生产总值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">108</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元，规模工业增加值达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">64</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元，地方一般预算收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">4.4</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元。而这三项指标，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2005</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年分别只有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">32.36</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">7</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">0.9</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿元。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">经济飞速发展的同时，嘉鱼先后投资</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">7</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">亿多元，用于改善城市人居环境，建设幸福之城。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">沙滩浴场、人民公园、二乔公园、沿湖景观带相继建成，免费向市民开放，过去仅有几个公共文体娱乐场所，现在达到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多个。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">京港澳高速连接线，武嘉一级公路，城区发展大道、迎宾大道相继建成通车；老城区主次干道刷黑、人行道改造；全面&ldquo;禁麻&rdquo;、&ldquo;禁摩&rdquo;，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">60</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多台公交车、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">200</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多台出租车穿街过巷。嘉鱼人民出行更畅通，更方便。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">主次干道全部实施亮化、绿化、美化工程；平安城市视频监控系统覆盖大街小巷；城市生活污水截流管网全面落成，并新建污水处理厂等。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">城市功能越来越完善了，城市越来越美了。以前不知道邀客人来玩什么的嘉鱼人，如今逢年过节，总喜欢请亲戚朋友过来转一转、看一看。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">全民参与创建</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">揽获国字号&ldquo;金字招牌&rdquo;，嘉鱼人感到无比豪迈。但翻开</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">8</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年创建历史，殊不知，文明创建之初，部分干部有怨气，部分群众不理解。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">县直机关单位不仅要出力，还要出钱，行动不力还要受通报批评，不免有怨气。出店占道经营的摊主，遇到创建整治队员，总是有抵触情绪，创建有难度，矛盾重重。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">随着&ldquo;建设人民满意城市&rdquo;目标的提出。一项项民生工程改善人们的生活，一缕缕民生福祉润泽人民心田。创建的实效消解了怨气，赢得了民心。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">少则</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">10</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">来万，多则上百万的投入，使县直单位办公条件、服务设施改善了，居住环境改变了，对外形象提升了，收入水平也随着经济的发展逐步提升。创建的怨气没了。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">城市环境看得见、摸得着的变化，让老百姓得到了吃、住、行等方方面面的实惠。群众对创建越来越主动了。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">80</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">岁的胡大爷，每天必做的一件事情就是拿着笔记本到街上转一转，哪里不干净，哪里设施有破损，他都逐一记录下来，然后来到创建办&ldquo;问责&rdquo;。退休干部舒老曾带着自己拍摄的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">100</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多张有损城市形象的照片，来到县创建办，提出整改要求和建议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">在创建工作中，嘉鱼县建立了整套完善的运行机制，覆盖了企事业单位、学校、社区及社会团体。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多名县级领导挂帅，包路段、包区域，当&ldquo;街长&rdquo;、当&ldquo;路长&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">6</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">名主要县领导担任县城及周边</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">6</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">个社区第一书记；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">220</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">名市容监督员走街串巷，乐当&ldquo;和事佬&rdquo;；&ldquo;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">10</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">分钟文明早课&rdquo;成为学生们每天的必修课&hellip;&hellip;</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">&ldquo;现在，不维护创建成果，嘉鱼人民都不答应。&rdquo;县创建全国文明县城指挥部办公室常务副主任雷申会说。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">幸福指数倍增</font></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">谈及文明创建的成果，&ldquo;老嘉鱼&rdquo;赵帮国一脸幸福地说：&ldquo;没有创建，就没有嘉鱼人民今天舒心惬意的生活环境。&rdquo;</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2004</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼着手创建省级文明县城，次年被省委、省政府命名为&ldquo;省级文明县城&rdquo;，并连续３届获此殊荣。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼荣获&ldquo;全国平安建设先进县&rdquo;、&ldquo;省级园林县城&rdquo;称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2010</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，获得&ldquo;国家级食品安全示范县&rdquo;、&ldquo;全国绿化模范县&rdquo;称号。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年初，嘉鱼获评&ldquo;省级卫生县城&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2011</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年底，嘉鱼摘得&ldquo;全国文明县城&rdquo;桂冠。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">短短</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">8</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">年，嘉鱼完成了从一个小城到省级文明卫生县城再到全国文明县城的完美跨越，先后获得全国、省、市文明单位荣誉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">30</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">余个。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">&ldquo;蔬菜大县&rdquo;、&ldquo;螃蟹之乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;黄金之乡&rdquo;、&ldquo;t鱼之乡&rdquo;的美誉实至名归。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">嘉鱼人感叹：创建让他们享受到了实实在在的福祉。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">人均纯收入年增</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">700</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">元左右，群众对每年政府承诺实事落实情况测评满意率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">98%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">，群众对政风行风满意率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">98%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">，群众对社会治安满意率达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">96%</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">各种内容健康、形式多样、丰富多彩的群众性文体活动越来越多，今年仅在二乔公园就开展了元宵灯会、拔河比赛、歌咏比赛、摄影展、根雕沙龙等活动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">多场。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">过去羡慕武汉、羡慕温泉，如今越来越多的外地客商来到嘉鱼兴业，越来越多的外地务工人员纷纷回乡创业，而且每年都有武汉市民到嘉鱼买房定居。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">&ldquo;全国文明县城的桂冠，不只是一个梦想的实现，对嘉鱼人来说，更是一段幸福新征程的开启。&rdquo;县长余珂说，要巩固好文明创建的成果，真正把嘉鱼建成人人向往的地方。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1222','284','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2011-12-31/267a99fb30b6b0769387648a1c27c488.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">座谈会现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">倾听企业呼声，优化发展环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，嘉鱼县国土资源局开门治庸问责，主动接受评议，邀请人大代表、政协委员及企业代表召开治庸问责座谈会。县委常委、政法委书记朱从钦，副县长李德炳出席座谈会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，县国土局局长吴鹏汇报了该局治庸问责工作开展情况。该局在治庸问责工作中，以治理为重点，坚持加强对党员干部的学习教育，认真开展自查自纠活动；坚持&ldquo;问题导向&rdquo;，以发现和解决问题为主导，围绕重点范围、重点领域、重点岗位、重点对象，深入查找突出问题；坚持严格问责，以领导班子和中层干部为重点，对暴露和反映的突出问题，认真调查核实，依据相关规定，划清责任，实施行政问责。下一阶段，该局将进一步以服务企业服务发展的水平检验&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;的成效。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">联乐集团、田野集团、中能锂电、葛洲坝水泥等十多家受邀企业代表分别作了发言，对县国土局服务企业推动发展的情况提出意见和建议。代表们充分肯定该局&ldquo;一站式服务、一个窗口对外&rdquo;的服务模式，尤其是该局大力推行的预约服务、延时服务，上门服务，超前服务、在线服务等人性化服务方式，为企业办事提供了极大方便。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">朱从钦在会上讲话，他要求县国土局认真吸纳各代表、委员、企业家提出的意见和建议，提前谋划</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年各项工作，进一步提升凝聚力和服务意识；简化和规范审批程序，优化审批流程，规范行政行为，提高审批效能；以治庸问责为契机，促使国土服务水平更加优质高效。<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1223','284','汪姝琴','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2012-01-01/9ebb1f975b698d8f71cc415c8542a337.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: x-small\\\\\">图为会议现场</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县委宣传部召开治庸问责自查整改民主生活会，全体机关干部对自身存在的&ldquo;庸懒散软</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&rdquo;</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">等现象进行了自查，并针对存在的问题拟定了整改计划，民主生活会上气氛热烈。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委常委、宣传部长刘合权参与讨论，并就干部们存在的共性问题，指出今后努力的方向，提出&ldquo;四勤四会&rdquo;，要求全体机关干部要进一步端正工作态度，提升能力水平，勤动手、勤动口、勤动脚、勤动脑，会写、会说、会办事、会协调。通过治庸问责工作，努力建设&ldquo;四型机关&rdquo;，即学习型机关、人文型机关、务实型机关、创新型机关，让全县宣传思想水平更上一台阶。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">通过民主生活会推进治庸问责工作，该部全体机关干部在自查整改中觉得心更齐了，劲更足了，工作目标更明确了，决心在来年的工作中做出自己的工作成绩。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1224','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-01-01/5c6c21a445625444f3a0b30cef1b4ba5.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">舞蹈《开门红》演出现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"color: black; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;敬爱的老同志们，可爱的小朋友们，我们来看你们了！&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31</span>日，一场主题为&ldquo;情系福利中心&rdquo;的迎春文艺慰问演出走进嘉鱼县社会福利中心，为福利院的老人和孩子们带来了社会的关爱和新年的祝福。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">该慰问演出由县民政局主办，县老年人体协、县关心下一代工作委员会、县老区建设促进会和县书法协会协办。来自县民乐演唱团、戏迷协会、夕阳红文体队、县健身球协会的演员们不仅带来了腰鼓、舞蹈、管乐演奏、歌曲演唱等精彩节目，还专门为福利院的老人们量身打造，献上了他们最喜欢的《军民鱼水情》、《贵妃醉酒》、《铡美案》等京剧选段，赢得大家阵阵掌声。县书法协会还向福利院赠送了春节对联和书画作品。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;福利院里好久没有这么热闹了，今天我们都从房里出来看节目了，心里高兴得很啊。&rdquo;年过八旬的寄养老人李秀英掩饰不住心里的喜悦向记者说道。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;祝愿福利院的老人们都能过上一个幸福的晚年，孩子们都能过上一个快乐的童年。&rdquo;县人大副主任、县老干部局局长戴书萍号召社会各界都来关心老人、小孩等弱势群体，在全社会营造起敬老爱小的和谐氛围。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">据了解，嘉鱼县社会福利中心是全县唯一的国办社会福利机构，服务对象主要是辖区内的孤寡老人、孤寡优抚对象、社会弃婴、自费托养老人等，现有住院院民<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80</span>多人。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/