E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1225','6','李发扬、江开群、张旭','咸宁日报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">市第四次党代会后，嘉鱼县围绕明年生产总值增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">18%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，地方一般预算收入增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，规模工业增加值突破</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">80</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元的目标，把项目建设作为建设&ldquo;湖北经济强县、长江临港新城&rdquo;的重要突破口，加大惠民利民工程建设力度，切实保障民生，以大发展迎接新开局。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">项目是经济发展的重要载体。该县以发展为第一要务，大抓项目，抓大项目。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">党代会召开后，该县迅速组织召开县&ldquo;四大家&rdquo;联席会议，对全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">50</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个涉及工业、农业、旅游、城建交通、社会发展等领域的重点项目，落实县级联点领导和责任单位，明确建设内容和完成进度。为突出抓好事关全县经济发展和民生的重点项目，分别成立了经济开发区二期、旅游开发、文体会展中心、嘉鱼大道建设、城区三环线建设等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重点项目建设指挥部，组建了咸宁嘉鱼长江大桥、武汉新港嘉鱼港区、武深高速、咸嘉新城等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个重大项目前期工作推进领导小组。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%\\\\